{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/html/html-pages/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Since HTML is used to structure entire web pages, then let's write one!</p>\n<p>Open the same index.html file we used in the previous post and delete everything in it.</p>\n<p>Then write the following:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>This is the HTML element, which is used to mark the beginning and the end of an HTML webpage. All of the content within HTML files should be \"wrapped\" with these tags.</p>\n<p>Then add an opening and closing tag for the <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;head&gt;</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;body&gt;</code> elements, like this:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h1>The Head</h1>\n<p>Is the element where you define all of the information that the page needs to have, but doesn't need to show on the page. Like the title of the page, that shows up in the actual tab in your browser and search results. </p>\n<h1>The Body</h1>\n<p>The body holds all of the content that has to be shown on the page. Like headings, paragraphs, lists and links, and many more.</p>\n<h1>Putting it all together</h1>\n<p>By now we already know enough to construct a very simple HTML page. Let's take the setup we already have and start adding content to it.</p>\n<p>First, let's add a page title, in the <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;head&gt;</code> element, like so:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>My Page Title!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  \n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Now you should see the title of the page switch to whatever is the content in the element.</p>\n<p>Now let's add a heading, you can also add a list and a few links if you'd like. I'll only add the heading.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>My Page Title!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>My Heading!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h1>Paragraphs</h1>\n<p>One of the most commonly used elements, the paragraph element: <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;p&gt;</code>. </p>\n<p>It's very similiar to the elements we've already used before. You just provide the opening and closing tag and the content between the tags.</p>\n<p>So let's add a paragraph, just beneath the heading and some <a href=\"https://www.lipsum.com/\">random text</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>My Page Title!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>My Heading!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nunc dui \n      leo, lobortis quis orci quis, tincidunt volutpat neque. Orci \n      varius natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur\n       ridiculus mus.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Additionally, you might want to split the paragraph into multiple lines, so you can use the line break element - <code class=\"language-html\"><br></code>. This one is a little different, it doesn't need a closing tag, because it doesn't hold any content by itself, it's just a line break.</p>\n<p>So let's add it to see what it does.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>My Page Title!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>My Heading!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nunc dui \n      leo, lobortis quis orci quis, <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>tincidunt volutpat neque. Orci \n      varius natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur\n       ridiculus mus.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>If you'd like to split the paragraph in multiple parts, i'd suggest using separate paragraph elements, to keep the syntax clean and not stack these breaks for adding whitespace.</p>\n<p>There's another element, that is quite similiar, the horizontal line element: <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;hr&gt;</code>. </p>\n<p>It also doesn't need a closing tag, because it's just a line. Let's add it to separate the heading and paragraph.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>My Page Title!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>My Heading!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>hr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nunc dui \n      leo, lobortis quis orci quis, <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>tincidunt volutpat neque. Orci \n      varius natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur\n       ridiculus mus.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h1>Final Render</h1>\n<iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"300\" src=\"//jsfiddle.net/itshazy/me3nd6vh/embedded/html,result/dark/\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" allowpaymentrequest frameborder=\"0\"></iframe>\n<p>Great! We'll take a look at how to establish layout in the next post.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"HTML Pages","index":1}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"excerpt":"HTML or Hyper Text Markup Language serves as the backbone that holds all of the content of any webpage. Literally all of them. \"Even giants…","fields":{"slug":"/html/what-is-html/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-02-23T00:00:00.000Z","title":"What is HTML?","categories":["HTML"],"index":0},"timeToRead":3}},{"node":{"excerpt":"Since HTML is used to structure entire web pages, then let's write one! Open the same index.html file we used in the previous post and…","fields":{"slug":"/html/html-pages/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-02-23T00:00:00.000Z","title":"HTML Pages","categories":["HTML"],"index":1},"timeToRead":3}},{"node":{"excerpt":"In the previous post we looked at the different elements that are most commonly used in websites. Let’s talk about layout. Obviously, after…","fields":{"slug":"/html/html-layout-and-styles/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-02-23T00:00:00.000Z","title":"HTML Layout and Styles","categories":["HTML"],"index":2},"timeToRead":11}},{"node":{"excerpt":"Previously we wrote styles directly on HTML elements. That is not the most convenient way, because imagine managing 50 files like those and…","fields":{"slug":"/html/intro-to-css-and-separation-of-concerns/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-02-24T00:00:00.000Z","title":"Intro to CSS and Separation of Concerns","categories":["HTML"],"index":3},"timeToRead":3}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/html/html-pages/","category":"HTML","index":1}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}